The paper proposes a tool for facilitating the development of data science scripts, which involves data manipulation and analysis. This falls under the domain of database systems (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). The tool also supports code completion in mainstream IDEs and editors, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning frameworks (cs.LG) and the conversion of implementations between frameworks, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
